      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JASPER ONE (6) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 22.94 beating Love Me Luna. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. GAME CHANGER (4) finished well back at Bendigo last time when a 9 length seventh (24.40) but scored three back at this track (22.83). Has a good winning strike rate at this journey. The form from his last run stacks up well. Leading chance. TRACK THIRTEEN (2) missed the frame last time but just three runs back was a strong Bottom Up - Restricted Win winner (22.85) at this track over 400m. Well placed here and should do much better. PAW YENNARA (7) will run well despite no experience on this track.",
